    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "拒绝抽样（Rejection Sampling）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            740,
            240
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目的：从 $p(x)$ 中抽取样本",
        "bbox": [
            91,
            320,
            457,
            400
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法：从 $g(x)$ 中抽取样本，并按一定的概率接收",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            485,
            796,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "要求: 存在 $M$ , 使得 $p(x) \\leq M g(x)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            651,
            594,
            729
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "步骤 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            196,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1. 从 $g(x)$ 中抽取样本, 并记为 $x^{*}$ ",
            "2. 计算 $r = \\frac{p\\left(x^{*}\\right)}{M g\\left(x^{*}\\right)}$ , 并从 $U[0,1]$ 中抽取 $u$ ",
            "3. 若 $u \\leq r$ , 则令 $x = x^{*}$ 即为从 $p(x)$ 中抽取的样本; 否则重复1.和2."
        ],
        "bbox": [
            81,
            320,
            905,
            907
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明：总体思路",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            444,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "考虑 $x$ 的分布函数:",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            296,
            321,
            355
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} F (t) = P (x \\leq t) = P \\left(x ^ {*} \\leq t \\mid \\text {接 收}\\right) = \\frac {P \\left(x ^ {*} \\leq t , \\text {接 收}\\right)}{P (\\text {接 收})} \\\\ = \\frac {P (x ^ {*} \\leq t , u \\leq r)}{P (u \\leq r)} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            168,
            420,
            833,
            751
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明: 分子",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            347,
            238
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} P (x ^ {*} \\leq t, u \\leq r) = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} \\left\\{\\int_ {0} ^ {p (x ^ {*}) / [ M g (x ^ {*}) ]} 1 \\cdot d u \\right\\} g (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} \\\\ = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} \\frac {p (x ^ {*})}{M g (x ^ {*})} \\times g (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} = \\frac {1}{M} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            150,
            329,
            850,
            683
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明：分母",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            347,
            238
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} P (u \\leq r) = P (- \\infty <   x ^ {*} <   + \\infty , u \\leq r) \\\\ = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} \\left\\{\\int_ {0} ^ {p (x ^ {*}) / [ M g (x ^ {*}) ]} 1 \\cdot d u \\right\\} g (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} \\\\ = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} \\frac {p (x ^ {*})}{M g (x ^ {*})} \\times g (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} = \\frac {1}{M} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} = \\frac {1}{M} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            177,
            300,
            827,
            772
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明：结论",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            347,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} F (t) = P (x \\leq t) = \\frac {P (x ^ {*} \\leq t , u \\leq r)}{P (u \\leq r)} = \\frac {\\frac {1}{M} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*}}{\\frac {1}{M}} \\\\ = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
